'''
SELECT acquiring.name AS buyer, 
       acq.price_amount AS transaction_amount, 
       acquired.name AS bought,    
       acquired.funding_total AS amount_investments,    
       ROUND(acq.price_amount/acquired.funding_total) AS ratio
FROM acquisition AS acq
LEFT JOIN company AS acquiring ON acquiring.id = acq.acquiring_company_id
LEFT JOIN company AS acquired ON acquired.id = acq.acquired_company_id
WHERE acq.price_amount > 0 AND acquired.funding_total > 0
ORDER BY acq.price_amount DESC, acquired.name
LIMIT 10;
'''

'''
WITH fund AS
    (SELECT EXTRACT(MONTH FROM CAST(fr.funded_at AS date)) AS month,
            COUNT(DISTINCT(f.name)) AS funds
     FROM funding_round AS fr
     INNER JOIN investment AS i ON fr.id = i.funding_round_id
     INNER JOIN fund AS f ON i.fund_id = f.id
     WHERE f.country_code = 'USA'
       AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CAST(fr.funded_at AS date)) 
           BETWEEN 2010 AND 2013
     GROUP BY month), 
     acquisition_tmp AS
    (SELECT EXTRACT(MONTH FROM CAST(acq.acquired_at AS date)) AS month,
            COUNT(acq.acquired_company_id) AS count,
            SUM(acq.price_amount) AS sum
     FROM acquisition AS acq
     WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CAST(acq.acquired_at AS date)) 
           BETWEEN 2010 AND 2013
     GROUP BY month)
SELECT ac.month, 
       ac.funds, 
       acquis.count, 
       acquis.sum
FROM acquisition_tmp AS acquis
JOIN fund AS ac ON acquis.month = ac.month
'''

'''
WITH year_2011 AS (
    SELECT country_code AS country, 
           AVG(funding_total) AS avg_2011
    FROM company
    WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CAST(founded_at AS date)) = 2011
    GROUP BY country_code),

    year_2012 AS (
    SELECT country_code AS country, 
           AVG(funding_total) AS avg_2012
    FROM company
    WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CAST(founded_at AS date)) = 2012
    GROUP BY country_code),

    year_2013 AS (
    SELECT country_code AS country, 
           AVG(funding_total) AS avg_2013
    FROM company
    WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CAST(founded_at AS date)) = 2013
    GROUP BY country_code)

SELECT year_2011.country, 
       year_2011.avg_2011, 
       year_2012.avg_2012, 
       year_2013.avg_2013
FROM year_2011
INNER JOIN year_2012 ON year_2011.country = year_2012.country
INNER JOIN year_2013 ON year_2011.country = year_2013.country
ORDER BY year_2011.avg_2011 DESC
